'''亚热带风暴阿尔法'''（{{lang-en|Subtropical Storm Alpha}}）曾于1972年5月吹袭[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]，是一场较为罕见的[[淡季大西洋热带气旋列表|淡季]][[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]。系统源于西大西洋形成的一个不具备热带天气系统特征的气旋，起初向东北方向移动至[[南卡罗莱纳州|南]]、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]近海。受逐渐成形的[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，风暴转向西南，同时增强成亚热带风暴并获名“阿尔法”。气旋之后从[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]附近海岸[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，最终于5月29日在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]东北部消散。阿尔法在沿海地区产生大浪和中等程度降水，导致两人丧生，损失总额超过10万美元（1972年[[美元|美元]]）。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Alpha 1972 track.png}}
1972年5月，连续多个弱[[低压槽|低压槽]]从[[美国东部|美国东部]]经过。这个月第三周，其中一个低压槽沿线在[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]发展出闭合形上层低气压，并与[[西风带|西风带]]相分离。阿尔法源于佛罗里达州东北部的下层低气压，这股低气压还同大规模冷芯上层低压相关联。<ref>{{cite report | author = Robert Dickson | year = 1972 | title = Weather and Circulation of May 1972 | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2015-12-29 | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/100/mwr-100-08-0648.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120604002000/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/100/mwr-100-08-0648.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-06-04 | format = PDF | date =  }}</ref><ref name="mwr">{{cite report | author1 = R.H. Simpson | author2 = Paul J. Hebert | date = 1973-04 | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1972 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-12-29 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1972.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925071608/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1972.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2015-09-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>系统经过组织，于5月23日晚在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]和[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]边界以东洋面发展成[[亚热带气旋|亚热带低气压]]<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151208052624/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | deadurl = no | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2015-12-29 | title = Easy-to-Read HURDAT 1851–2008 | archivedate = 2015-12-08 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html }}</ref>。行进至[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[哈特拉斯_(北卡罗莱纳州)|哈特拉斯]]（{{lang|en|Hatteras}}）东南方向海域时，气旋因受逐渐成形的高压脊影响而无法再向东北方向前进，然后缓慢转向东南。5月25日，系统内快速形成规模虽小但强度较高的下层中心，到次日就已达到烈风强度，并且这时还已转朝西南方向移动。<ref name="mwr" />[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]5月26日下午16点，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始针对位于[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）以南约362公里海域的亚热带气旋阿尔法发布公告<ref name="mar1">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Marine Bulletin Number 1 | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | archivedate = 2015-12-08 | format = JPG | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151208052624/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/MARINE/MARADV261600Z.JPG }}</ref>，风暴还在几乎同一时间达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时110公里的最高强度<ref name="HURDAT" />。

美国国家飓风中心针对风暴的首份公告显示，多个预测模型对气旋最终的移动路线存在分歧，有些认为系统会登陆乔治亚州，有些则认为会向东北方向前进，逐渐远离陆地<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = May 26 Forecast | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235044/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/MISC/FCST261200Z.JPG | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/MISC/FCST261200Z.JPG }}</ref>。阿尔法的气候特点也较为反常，美国国家飓风中心当时没有找到任何类似风暴的过往纪录<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Forecast Models on May 27 | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235056/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/MODELOUT/CLIPER270000Z.JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/MODELOUT/CLIPER270000Z.JPG }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Bernard N. Meisner | year = 2006 | title = An Overview of the NHC Prediction Models | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/ssd/nwpmodel/html/nhcmodel.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150921221601/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/ssd/nwpmodel/html/nhcmodel.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-09-21 }}</ref>。气旋起初向西南方向移动，组织结构层次分明。系统中心位于对流东部边缘，规模非常小，东面还有下层云系形成<ref name="mwr" /><ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Satellite Weather Bulletin | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235119/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/SATCWS/MSB262340Z.JPG | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/SATCWS/MSB262340Z.JPG }}</ref>。气旋这时的温度结构更接近冬季风暴，但由于这时已是夏季，气象机构估计系统会朝亚热带风暴转变<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Bulletin One | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235128/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB261600Z.JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB261600Z.JPG }}</ref>。5月27日，风暴略向西面转向，风速也稳步下降，暴雨主要在中心以东和以北持续<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Bulletin One | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB271600Z.JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235128/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB261600Z.JPG }}</ref>。

美国国家飓风中心起初起初认为，风暴中心可能并不属下层中心，但由于无法确定环流中心的存在，该机构对预测并不是很有把握<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Internal Office Advisory on Alpha | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235143/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/SATCWS/SAW271330Z.JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/SATCWS/SAW271330Z.JPG }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Internal Office Advisory on Alpha | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235153/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/SATCWS/SAW271854Z.JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/SATCWS/SAW271854Z.JPG }}</ref>。这种情况的出现主要是因为风暴规模非常庞大，直至5月27日晚才经雷达图像和[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机确认有中心形成<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Bulletin Five | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB271800Z.JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235201/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB271800Z.JPG }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Bulletin Seven | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235213/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB272200Z.01.JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB272200Z.01.JPG }}</ref>。当晚，阿尔法的中心从[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]以南不远处登陆，以风速每小时100公里、最低气压991[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.26[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）强度对小范围区域构成影响<ref name="mwr" />。风暴还在登陆前后发展出暖芯，这表明系统已经拥有部分热带天气系统特征<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235037/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/OPLTRACK/TRACK1.JPG | title = Tentative Best Track: "Alpha" 1972 | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/OPLTRACK/TRACK1.JPG | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | format = JPG }}</ref>。阿尔法在陆地上空迅速减弱，于两天后在墨西哥湾东北部上空完全消散<ref name="HURDAT" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Alpha_1972_rainfall.png|thumb]]
美国国家飓风中心针对阿尔法发布首份公告时，[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[杰克逊维尔_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔]]到[[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[开普梅_(新泽西州)|开普梅]]之间地区接获小型船只警告；北卡罗莱纳州[[恐怖角_(北卡罗莱纳州)|恐怖角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Fear}}）到[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]][[阿可麦克县_(弗吉尼亚州)|阿可麦克县]][[钦科蒂格_(弗吉尼亚州)|钦科蒂格]]（{{lang|en|Chincoteague}}）之间地区还收到烈风警告<ref name="mar1" />。风暴与东北方向的[[高气压|高气压]]系统相互影响，导致气温降低的同时，还有大风从[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]南下，弗吉尼亚海角沿线的海浪最高达到6.1米。<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | title = Special Weather Statement | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235221/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/LOCAL/DCA261810Z.JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/LOCAL/DCA261810Z.JPG }}</ref>气旋在北卡罗莱纳州和弗吉尼亚州沿海产生暴雨，降雨量最高的[[奥克拉科克_(北卡罗莱纳州)|奥克拉科克]]（{{lang|en|Ocracoke}}）达到177毫米<ref name="HPC">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150210082139/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alpha1972.html | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | title = Subtropical Storm Alpha – May 23–29, 1972 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alpha1972.html | archivedate = 2015-02-10 }}</ref>。行经北卡罗莱纳州近海期间，阿尔法引发严重的海滩侵蚀，摧毁了一套房屋，还对[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]多套民宅的根基构成威胁，造成的破坏总额超过5万美元（1972年美元）<ref name="ncdc">{{cite journal | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | title = Storm Data May 1972 | volume = 14 | number = 5 | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-AF7C8C40-7DD3-4793-A17A-590D44898E0D.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2015-12-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151230151757/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-AF7C8C40-7DD3-4793-A17A-590D44898E0D.pdf | journal =  }}[http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html 此网站] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html |date=20160414065723 }}可查询美国国家海洋和大气管理局风暴数据平面出版物的内容，查询结果链接有效时间为24小时，用户可选择“1972-05”获得所需要的信息。</ref>。阿尔法行经西大西洋期间令大范围海域波涛汹涌，恶劣的海况被视为这场风暴引起的最大威胁<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Bulletin One | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235228/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB270400Z.JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB270400Z.JPG }}</ref>。

佛罗里达州东北部有警务人员在海滩驻守，防止人们前往危险的水域游泳，大浪还令[[梅波特海军基地|梅波特海军基地]]一座港口的开挖加深工作被迫暂停<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | year = 1972 | title = Cyclone Serves Notice of Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | newspaper = The Tuscaloosa News | via = Google News Archive Search | url = https://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=1WI0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=L5wEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4138,4676389&dq=storm+1972+georgia+may&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-12-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201209030640/https://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=1WI0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=L5wEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4138%2C4676389&dq=storm+1972+georgia+may&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴消散后，海上依然波涛汹涌，有两人因此溺毙<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Palm Beach Post | date = 1972-05 | title = Four Drown in Area Mishaps}}</ref>。乔治亚州沿海的潮汐比正常水平要高0.61至0.91米，引发一定程度的洪水和海滩侵蚀<ref name="ncdc" /><ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Severe Weather Statement | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | archivedate = 2015-07-08 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708190723/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/LOCAL/SAV280025Z.JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/LOCAL/SAV280025Z.JPG }}</ref>。[[圣西蒙斯_(乔治亚州)|圣西蒙斯岛]]（{{lang|en|Saint Simons Island}}）的阵风时速有93公里<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1972 | title = Bulletin Eight | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708181920/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB280200Z.JPG | archivedate = 2015-07-08 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB280200Z.JPG }}</ref>。大风刮倒部分树木，还令多条输电线缆中断，乔治亚州东部部分居民家中停电。该州所受破坏程度较轻，但范围甚广，估计数额超过5万美元（1972年美元）<ref name="ncdc" />。此外，南卡罗莱纳州到佛罗里达州南部都出现中等程度降水<ref name="HPC" />。

阿尔法是以[[北约音标字母|北约音标字母]]命名，[[1972年大西洋飓风季|1972年大西洋飓风季]]由此成为历史上第一个有非热带气旋获命名的飓风季。当时大型亚热带气旋和中性热带气旋都是以这种方式命名，之后再合并成一个分类。<ref name="mwr" />

